chool football team is one of the most successful in texas with a game winning streak individuals who wish to pursue a university degree can attend the nearby university of north texas or the university of texas at dallas those keen on reading and furthering their research will love the celina public library downtown celina is a lively place which boasts excellent stores and restaurants the historic square is a pedestrianfriendly area and the spot where many community events take place residents can also visit nearby shopping malls such as the prestonbrook crossing the village at fairview is a large mall located nearby offering over  stores many restaurants and numerous entertainment options the city features three excellent parks old celina park is celinas crown jewel and includes an awardwinning baseball complex soccer fields a pavilion a playground and a fishing pond  perfect for family gatherings residents can also easily reach the ray roberts lake state park a wonderful natural oasis where one can enjoy swimming boating picnicking and kayaking celina is one of those rare places that still has that unique smalltown charm to it with excellent amenities notable schools and great shopping opportunities celina is the perfect place for living regardless of your age occupation and interests this warm community will make you feel at home in this city residents who wish to relocate to this city can refer to new home source in order to find great offers in celina the comprehensive listings of new home source will help home buyers find their perfect home in no time and even if you cant find your perfect match in celina our site can help you expand your search and find new homes in frisco or mckinney or even search all the new real estate in dallas clear all filters location location search searching map area x radius exact  mi exact location cancel update price price min to max cancel update beds  baths bedrooms all      bathrooms all      cancel update schools school dis